@node "Preface" "SLIPCall Users Guide"

@{b} Preface@{ub}
@{b} ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ@{ub}

  SLIPCall is offered to you under the concepts of FreeWare. You can use it
  as long as you like without paying any charge.

  If you want, you can register by sending me a postcard, or even a simple
