@node "Main Project Quit" "SLIPCall Users Guide"

@{b} Quit
 ŻŻŻŻ@{ub}

Keyboard short-cut: Right Amiga Q  (Main Window: Q for Quit button)

  Quit SLIPCall. If you're still online, SLIPCall will ask you to confirm.

  When waiting for redial, Quit immediatly aborts waiting and dialing, and
  returns to initial state.



