@node "Main Action Resume" "SLIPCall Users Guide"

@{b} Resume
 ŻŻŻŻŻŻ@{ub}

Keyboard short-cut: Right Amiga R  (Main Window: R for Resume button)

  Tries to resume a lost connection. (i.e. due to a system crash, or
  something...) This choice is only available if something went really
  wrong with your connection.

  You can only resume a connection if the modem is still online!



@endnode

