@node "40" "SLIPCall Users Guide"

@{b} Release 4
 ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ@{ub}


    @{b}Version 37.51 (21.1.96)@{ub}

    - '\\' allowed in command strings.
    - BUGFIX: Correct IP extracted.
    - BUGFIX: Crashed when extracting IP address.
    - BUGFIX: Resume didn't work properly.


    @{b}Version 37.49 (11.1.96)@{ub}

    - Updated the Phonebill scanner to a working version.
    - Added Terminal and Requester menu choices
    - BUGFIX: Resume didn't work.
    - BUGFIX: Gadget states properly set when starting without opening window.
    - BUGFIX: Don't execute mailcommands if net not found.
    - BUGFIX: Hopefully gets correct IP and don't crashes when scanning IP.
    - BUGFIX: Didn't support several CR's in a row in the script.
    - BUGFIX: PPP gets the correct IP at first time. ;)
    - BUGFIX: No system crash when modem unavailable anymore
    - BUGFIX: IP Settings handles 12-digit addresses correct.


    @{b}Version 37.47@{ub}

    Code completly rewritten in C!

    GUI rewritten, uses bgui.library.

    A completly new program!!



@endnode

